{"id":"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08","title":"第8课：使用 *ngFor 列出组件中的对象","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"lesson-8-use-ngfor-to-list-objects-in-component\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2n800r1o0v8vfx0gy4hw370bm\">第8课：使用 *ngFor 列出组件中的对象<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#lesson-8-use-ngfor-to-list-objects-in-component\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"980vjuhfa5oxnn8yvxdzktw1n\">本教程演示了如何在 Angular 模板中使用\n<code>ngFor</code>指令来动态显示重复数据。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9b0304m4wmxslkazn9h6yr4kn\"><strong>预计时间</strong>: 约10分钟</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3a5wqy6ph21q6b03b5hw7pmrf\"><strong>起始代码:</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-07\"></live-example></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7xc9i90tjljm5fk00thk6sxer\"><strong>完成代码:</strong> \n<live-example name=\"first-app-lesson-08\"></live-example></p>\n<h2 id=\"what-youll-learn\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cy8qhuh22qozu5okjmjfdf3nx\">你将学到<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#what-youll-learn\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"339lylyqh3j0rt2u8j4fmt872\">你将向应用程序添加一个数据集</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2ix7vbzf6lrzjuzshaqs53kt0\">应用程序将使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code> 显示新数据集中的元素列表</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"conceptual-preview-of-ngfor\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d26q8e1e7s57kw2f18x1wvikh\">ngFor 的概念性预览<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#conceptual-preview-of-ngfor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a465jko8c6cd4aun2bsy9rbp9\">在 Angular 中，\n<code>ngFor</code> 是一种特定类型的指令，用于在模板中动态重复数据。在纯JavaScript中，你会使用for循环 - ngFor为Angular模板提供了类似的功能。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"qn7w8wsxtng5yjsjkw7gt240\">你可以利用 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code> 来迭代数组甚至异步值。在这节课中，你将添加一个新的数据数组以进行迭代。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3ql8mt3nfqwrr6u8gx2drsn95\">更深入的解释，请参阅<a href=\"guide/built-in-directives#ngFor\">内置指令</a>指南。</p>\n<h2 id=\"step-1---add-housing-data-to-the-homecomponent\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"80crbki5zbysuifpxdhc1b8dd\">第 1 步 - 将房屋数据添加到 <code>HomeComponent</code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#step-1---add-housing-data-to-the-homecomponent\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"271isnksvtfl0ffe1bsw06iip\">在 <code>HomeComponent</code> 中只有一个房屋位置。在此步骤中，你将添加一组 <code>HousingLocation</code> 条目。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5gmlv896e5cpa82ff0c65gsrv\">在 <code>src/app/home/home.component.ts</code> 中，从 <code>HomeComponent</code> 类删除 <code>housingLocation</code> 属性。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"14it0crmvp48gcyv4cmkrm4bb\">更新\n<code>HomeComponent</code>类，添加一个名为\n<code>housingLocationList</code>的属性。更新你的代码以匹配以下代码： \n<code-example header=\"添加 housingLocationList 属性\" path=\"first-app-lesson-08/src/app/home/home.component.ts\" region=\"housing-list-entries\">\n  export class HomeComponent { readonly baseUrl = 'https://angular.io/assets/images/tutorials/faa'; housingLocationList: HousingLocation[] = [ { id: 0, name: 'Acme Fresh Start Housing', city: 'Chicago', state: 'IL', photo: `${this.baseUrl}/bernard-hermant-CLKGGwIBTaY-unsplash.jpg`, availableUnits: 4, wifi: true, laundry: true }, ... ]; } \n</code-example></p>\n<div class=\"callout is-important\">\n  Do not remove the `@Component` decorator, you will update that code in an upcoming step.\n</div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"step-2---update-the-homecomponent-template-to-use-ngfor\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6y3gkmg7p222d21xreq4xmgrp\">第 2 步 - 更新 <code>HomeComponent</code> 模板以使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#step-2---update-the-homecomponent-template-to-use-ngfor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3nj32te2vpzlozfpjwj2rps7c\">现在应用程序有一个数据集，你可以使用它来借助 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code> 指令在浏览器中显示条目。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4irkv3pmgu564j0k4siqyrtuh\">将模板代码中的\n<code>&lt;app-housing-location&gt;</code>标签更新为以下内容： \n<code-example header=\"向 HomeComponent 模板添加 ngFor\" path=\"first-app-lesson-08/src/app/home/home.component.ts\" region=\"add-ngFor\">\n  &lt;app-housing-location *ngFor=\"let housingLocation of housingLocationList\" [housingLocation]=\"housingLocation\"&gt; &lt;/app-housing-location&gt; \n</code-example></p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9qeo481sky0yqxm4ez1z71rwp\">请注意，在代码\n<code>[housingLocation] = \"housingLocation\"</code>中，\n<code>housingLocation</code>值现在指的是\n<code>ngFor</code>指令中使用的变量。在此更改之前，它指的是\n<code>HomeComponent</code>类上的属性。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7y9sibc49gz4j1owr3vr5a678\">保存所有更改。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"48ca0fbgsxlm1qlifktadhsgk\">刷新浏览器并确认应用程序现在渲染出了房屋位置网格。</p>\n<section class=\"lightbox\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8ikxk2koge8635i2rw7o9gqi2\"><img alt=\"browser frame of homes-app displaying logo, filter text input box, search button and a grid of housing location cards\" src=\"generated/images/guide/faa/homes-app-lesson-08-step-2.png\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1360\"></section>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"lesson-review\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ckmo8mg671uh3oxv2z72tuj64\">课程回顾<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#lesson-review\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7msewi4m3smuaj7xuax213b8g\">在这节课中，你使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code> 指令在 Angular 模板中动态重复渲染数据。你还添加了要在 Angular 应用程序中使用的新数据数组。该应用程序现在在浏览器中动态渲染房屋位置列表。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2772diwcsraygxhujks4bgfvp\">该应用程序正在成形，干得好。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2vi4aou9du2w1ijyabax7x8qx\">如果你在学习这节课时遇到了任何问题，可以在<live-example></live-example>查看完整代码。</p>\n<h2 id=\"next-steps\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c4pkljueu68ifjoi5994e9l8o\">下一步<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#next-steps\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c6fgyie3k43um6eh7x0e5s6vv\"><a href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-09\">第 9 课 - 向应用程序添加服务</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ep5mlw3d5q1ucm62jzem9a7pc\">有关这节课中涵盖的主题的更多信息，请访问：<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c9spl6m4xgippat8z0h2fgghz\"><a href=\"/guide/structural-directives\">结构型指令</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9sl9vswslscj4e0ijmhhxj4gi\"><a href=\"/guide/built-in-directives#ngFor\">ngFor 指南</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/api/common/NgFor\">ngFor</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间：Tue Jul 11 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api/common/NgFor\n - /guide/built-in-directives#ngFor\n - /guide/structural-directives\n - api/common/NgFor\n - guide/built-in-directives\n - guide/built-in-directives#ngFor\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#conceptual-preview-of-ngfor\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#for-more-information-about-the-topics-covered-in-this-lesson-visit\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#lesson-8-use-ngfor-to-list-objects-in-component\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#lesson-review\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#next-steps\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#step-1---add-housing-data-to-the-homecomponent\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#step-2---update-the-homecomponent-template-to-use-ngfor\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08#what-youll-learn\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-09\n-->"}